ibold text-gray-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors line-clamp-1\">埃斯特哈齐宫（海顿曾担任宫廷乐长、拥有绝佳声学效果的海顿大厅的巴洛克宫殿）</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 line-clamp-1\">Schloss Esterházy</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </a>\n            </div>",
